author: Jacob Davey
title: Nicki Minaj & Future Are Filming a “Secret” Video
text:
Nicki Minaj and Future are set to link up again on a new track for the first time since appearing on DJ Khaled’s Major Key single “Do You Mind”. Ensuring the upcoming collaboration remained “secret” by sharing to her 74.8 million Instagram followers, Nicki shared a short video of her and the most proactive rapper in the game at the minute alongside some photos of her from the shoot which you can check out below.
🎀 @future 🎬😜 
A post shared by Nicki Minaj (@nickiminaj) on Feb 27, 2017 at 2:24pm PST 

#PatekWars 🎥🎬 #Pluto

#AnotherOne 🎬- 📸: @grizzleemusic

#IssaNOTHERvideoSHOOT ❤️👅 
A post shared by Nicki Minaj (@nickiminaj) on Feb 27, 2017 at 12:18pm PST 

Minaj has been under fire recently from Remy Ma, who held no prisoners in her “shEther” diss that she released over the weekend. Ma was supposedly triggered by some of Minaj’s bars in her recent Gucci Mane collab, “Make Love”. Give a listen to the first great hip-hop beef of the year below.

Until Nicki issues a response, get the scoop on Future potentially releasing a THIRD new album in quick succession right here .
